00:02:45.800 --> 00:02:51.100
[Amit Varma]: events drove Muslims in India away from the mainstream, and how their politics was often

00:02:51.100 --> 00:02:56.600
[Amit Varma]: so disconnected from their social reality. Most of all, it shows us the insecurity that

00:02:56.600 --> 00:03:02.520
[Amit Varma]: Muslims feel in India today, and the vicious circle of mistrust and animosity that we seem

00:03:02.520 --> 00:03:04.080
[Amit Varma]: to be trapped within.

00:03:04.080 --> 00:03:08.600
[Amit Varma]: But there is also much in this book to take hope from. This conversation covers a lot

